        <section><!-- Adding a Template -->
            <title>Adding a Template</title>

<text>There are several important items missing from the
<emph>base-type</emph>. These are covered by <emph>Monstrous Templates</emph>
which add things such as <emph>mental attributes</emph> (and <smallcaps>Cha</smallcaps>!),
<emph>special abilities</emph>, and a description of the monster, including
any relavent interaction statistics, such as combat, elocution etc.</text>


        </section><!-- /Adding a Template -->
